{"type": "article", "id": 2531, "title": "Alessi 餐桌装饰品", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-24T08:22:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232557q6j3MAy2IRYguFPX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t备受瞩目的 Campana 兄弟档设计师日前为意大利家居品牌 Alessi 带来一款名为“ Vime ”的餐桌装饰品，由藤条编制而成，底座部分可以用作果盘，中间凸起的中空部分可以插入鲜花、干花等，打造不同的效果。因为是纯手工制作的缘故，因此每一款“ Vime ”都将是独一无二的。售价 175 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.einrichten-design.de/en/vime-centerpiece-alessi.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232555dF1Vvh8OlizA2Yum.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232556puPBM9XRvsFYV83K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}